;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d989e1870254881e1d14ff8630ac64a23b7b4616","tid":1510113,"uid":8308,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a3e385bed8dcc2bd6d0efcbf8058f5863f977f33","tid":1510113,"uid":207734,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T05:24:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T06:17:46.000Z","msg":"去馬來西亞不如去大灣區<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大陸人都仲有反共 <br />\n馬拉華人真係奶共奶到傻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f77a1f3ac8af7453fd4836e218c4bbd4744deef0","tid":1510113,"uid":74185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T06:20:01.000Z","msg":"大馬不嬲好多撐中<br />\n你好多d Fb page都見到佢地蹤影<br />\n但佢地乜撚都唔知<br />\n同埋算啦<br />\n真正行出黎既香港人件事未完根本唔會移民，<br />\n唔係錢同資格問題。<br />\n係呢個時候會揀走既都係d口講反送中但又唔行出黎果批同埋d藍絲，<br />\n講就話愛香港，又得走就走夾唔抖。"},{"pid":"afeaf0ebc61cdd40b7fc1f50d25cbac68462d5be","tid":1510113,"uid":40624,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T06:20:05.000Z","msg":"我D馬拉親戚都係奶共<br />\n話咩 自己個根係中國<br />\n我通常即串佢,咁鍾意中國快D放棄大馬護照啦返中國住,即刻冇聲出<br />\n利申 馬來西亞人"},{"pid":"43398d2f1ec44a556769d6066bbdabc6d06d23e1","tid":1510113,"uid":156891,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T06:21:39.000Z","msg":"香港淪陷，移民去台灣一定最好<br />\n<br />\n當然台灣都唔安全，一樣面對赤化危機，好大機會淪陷<br />\n<br />\n但作為生於香港、熱愛香港既香港人，我立志終身與中共邪惡極權為敵，站於全球抗共最前線"},{"pid":"b406ad4d87e0d613b09af078b328f3d34a574df8","tid":1510113,"uid":32586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T06:27:18.000Z","msg":"第二家園無護照把撚咩"},{"pid":"92919a6f4def19337fe04f5d28940a4cf989e645","tid":1510113,"uid":208376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T06:33:23.000Z","msg":"大馬d樓已經多到賣唔出，大陸人換唔到錢買，仲出口術趕客<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n馬拉人智慧真係低華人最少一班"},{"pid":"b321143f35343382243e7b16611ad86a19a571c9","tid":1510113,"uid":295275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T06:35:07.000Z","msg":"Ok 886"},{"pid":"e45a22bbac42e26a45a4f475e6ded42704be93ab","tid":1510113,"uid":197125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T06:35:55.000Z","msg":"大馬本身都唔係有自由嘅國家，只係民主少少咋嘛，移民去做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a69458011639d323fff0f04187e76f24e9a8fbe","tid":1510113,"uid":256019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T06:38:03.000Z","msg":"蘭花系啤梨呢排做好多移民馬拉中介，成日吹到馬拉好好，又話大選變天之後改變好多，開明過以前，睇佢今晚YouTube節目點兜先！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5afe335e568ff145287bf25e4b29b57779fbe846","tid":1510113,"uid":38757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e45a22bbac42e26a45a4f475e6ded42704be93ab","tid":1510113,"uid":197125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T06:35:55.000Z","msg":"大馬本身都唔係有自由嘅國家，只係民主少少咋嘛，移民去做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T06:41:03.000Z","msg":"新加坡, 俄羅斯都係 所以佢地實反對"}]}